original_title: SnapCube's Real-Time Fandub and the Vibes of Rude Mountain - Part 2
overview: A group of friends will find their preconceptions changed in ways they never thought possible as they learn more about the intricacies of Rude Mountain and the plans of their morally questionable friend Josh. The vibes are here, and there's nowhere left to hide.
title: SnapCube's Real-Time Fandub and the Vibes of Rude Mountain - Part 2
